<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-light">

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark shadow-sm">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold" href="/admin/dashboard">
                <i class="bi bi-speedometer2 me-2 text-warning"></i> UTN AdminPanel
            </a>
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                <span class="text-white me-3">Hola, <strong class="text-warning"><%= adminName %></strong></span>
                <a href="/logout" class="btn btn-outline-danger btn-sm">
                    <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-right"></i> Cerrar Sesión
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container my-5">
        <div class="row">
            
            <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                <div class="list-group shadow-sm">
                    <a href="/admin/dashboard" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action active bg-dark border-dark">
                        <i class="bi bi-house-door me-2"></i> Inicio
                    </a>
                    <a href="/admin/productos" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">
                        <i class="bi bi-box-seam me-2 text-secondary"></i> Gestión de Productos
                    </a>
                    <a href="/admin/logs" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">
                        <i class="bi bi-file-earmark-text me-2 text-secondary"></i> Historial de Logs
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-9">
                
                <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded shadow-sm mb-4 border-start border-4 border-warning">
                    <h1 class="h2 mb-2">Panel de Control General</h1>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-0">Bienvenido al sistema de administración híbrido. Desde acá controlás el inventario que consume la API del cliente.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="row">
                    
                    <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                        <div class="card border-0 bg-primary text-white shadow-sm h-100">
                            <div class="card-body d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between">
                                <div>
                                    <h6 class="text-uppercase mb-1" style="font-size: 0.8rem; opacity: 0.85;">Productos en Base de Datos</h6>
                                    <h2 class="display-6 mb-0 fw-bold"><%= totalProducts %></h2>
                                </div>
                                <i class="bi bi-database display-4 opacity-50"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-footer bg-black bg-opacity-10 border-0">
                                <a href="/admin/productos" class="text-white text-decoration-none small d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between">
                                    <span>Ir a gestionar</span> <i class="bi bi-arrow-right-short"></i>
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                        <div class="card border-0 bg-success text-white shadow-sm h-100">
                            <div class="card-body d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between">
                                <div>
                                    <h6 class="text-uppercase mb-1" style="font-size: 0.8rem; opacity: 0.85;">Conexión MySQL</h6>
                                    <h2 class="h3 mb-0 fw-bold mt-2"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill me-2"></i>ONLINE</h2>
                                </div>
                                <i class="bi bi-cpu display-4 opacity-50"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-footer bg-black bg-opacity-10 border-0">
                                <span class="text-white small">Sincronizado con Sequelize</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>

                <div class="card mt-4 shadow-sm border-0">
                    <div class="card-header bg-white fw-bold py-3">
                        <i class="bi bi-info-circle text-primary me-2"></i> Resumen de Operación del Backend
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body class=text-secondary">
                        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Aliquid, quo.:</p>
                        <ul class="mb-0">
                            <li class="mb-2"><strong>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet.:</strong>Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Reprehenderit eveniet atque eaque perferendis, quam vero?</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><strong>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet.:</strong> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Dolores amet fugit voluptas fugiat mollitia repellat? <code class="bg-light px-2 py-1 rounded text-danger">Lorem</code> Lorem, ipsum dolor.</li>
                            <li><strong>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet.:</strong> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. At alias vel voluptatem architecto facilis possimus.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>